Overview:
This project aims to build a fully functional and scalable online marketplace where users can browse, buy, and sell furniture and crockery decoration items effortlessly. On Day 1, we are laying the foundation for the project, ensuring a solid structure that will support future enhancements.

Features:
✅ Scalable Modular Architecture – Designed to accommodate future updates smoothly.
✅ User-friendly Design – Ensuring a seamless browsing and shopping experience.
✅ Basic Frontend & Backend Setup – Establishing the core functionality of the marketplace.
✅ Placeholder Sections – Reserved for future features like user authentication and payment gateway integration.

Tech Stack:
🖥 Frontend: Next.js, React
🛠 Backend: Node.js, Express.js, Sanity
💾 Database: MongoDB, Firebase
🛠 Tools: TypeScript, Git, VS Code

Day 1 Objectives:
✅ Set up the project repository
✅ Define folder structure (e.g., components, pages, API, styles)
✅ Initialize package manager and install dependencies
✅ Create a basic landing page layout

